         <abstract id="aspace_54014bb13e957cc0ba0950a3f604539e">The Robert Davies papers on Hanson Baldwin contain correspondence, Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI) files, interview transcripts and audiocassettes relating to Davies's book: <title render="italic">
